channel.title: Rs2006
channel.description:
First off I'd like to say I take no credit for this, I'm simply releasing for other people to use and make something out of this. I've removed a lot of content, although I left the combat along with some of the basic stuff such as banking, shopping, trading; however all skills, functions (things like doors, object clicking, etc...) have been cleaned and removed.
There is a small anti-leech in here; very basic java knowledge will fix it.
Please do [B][I]not[/I][/B] post the anti-leech fix, thank you.
*snip*
